net.automatalib.serialization.automaton

Interface SimpleAutomatonSerializationProvider<S,I>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The state type of the de-serialized hypothesis
    I - The default input symbol type
    All Superinterfaces:
    InputModelDeserializer<I,SimpleAutomaton<S,I>>, InputModelSerializer<I,SimpleAutomaton<?,I>>, ModelDeserializer<InputModelData<I,SimpleAutomaton<S,I>>>, ModelSerializer<InputModelData<I,SimpleAutomaton<?,I>>>, SimpleAutomatonDeserializer<S,I>, SimpleAutomatonSerializer<I>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AUTSerializationProvider

    public interface SimpleAutomatonSerializationProvider<S,I>
extends SimpleAutomatonSerializer<I>, SimpleAutomatonDeserializer<S,I>
    A utility interface that unions SimpleAutomatonSerializer and SimpleAutomatonDeserializer.

    Note: These model-specific interfaces may be omitted if Java starts supporting higher-kinded generics (or we switch to a language that supports these).
